UPDATE orders SET 
  customerName = CASE 
    WHEN customerId % 10 = 0 THEN 'Jean-Pierre Mbarga'
    WHEN customerId % 10 = 1 THEN 'Marie Nguema'
    WHEN customerId % 10 = 2 THEN 'Paul Essomba'
    WHEN customerId % 10 = 3 THEN 'Fatou Diallo'
    WHEN customerId % 10 = 4 THEN 'Emmanuel Nkodo'
    WHEN customerId % 10 = 5 THEN 'Aissatou Bah'
    WHEN customerId % 10 = 6 THEN 'Christian Fotso'
    WHEN customerId % 10 = 7 THEN 'Mariama Sow'
    WHEN customerId % 10 = 8 THEN 'Pierre Atangana'
    ELSE 'Sophie Kamga'
  END,
  customerPhone = CONCAT('+237 6', LPAD(FLOOR(RAND() * 100000000), 8, '0')),
  customerEmail = CONCAT('customer', customerId, '@example.com')
